- Share your love of Albert with a friend
- New integrations with banks and lenders
- A few more goodies
To our dear 5s users, your income is fixed.
Speed improvements

- More speed improvements
- A few new illustrations
- Squashed some bugs

Albert 2.0 is here. We hope you enjoy using it as much as we enjoyed making it. Here's what's new:
- Albert Savings support for all US banks
- Insurance: auto insurance, life insurance, home and renter’s insurance
- New knowledge center and updated help center
- Personalized credit card finder
- New content, tips, alerts, and trends
- More granular notification controls
- Multiple properties
- Cars
- Student loans
- Speed improvements

- More control over savings: in addition to automatic savings, you can now set your own weekly amounts.
- Charting for spending: visit the budget section and any list of transactions to view a pie chart of historical spending by category or merchant
- New renter's insurance options
- Squashed some bugs

- Speed improvements
- Better visibility into account linking status
- Squashed a few bugs

- Brand new side menu
- Inbox to track financial products
- Updated tour
- New alerts
- Speed improvements

- New financial products
- Speed improvements

- Financial product updates
- Speed improvements

- Speed and bug fixes
- Financial product updates

- A more personal Albert
- Moved financial health sections to the main health screen, not sure why it was ever a swipe away
- Speed improvements
- Better recommendations
- Speed improvements and bug fixes
- A few product goodies

- home screen update
- powerful new alerts
- budgeting charting and tools
- subscriptions

- Speed improvements
- Bug fixes

Albert Genius is here!
A brand new experience, with the smartest, most powerful financial assistant around. A team of human financial geniuses, on demand, to guide you through your financial journey and answer your most complicated questions.
We hope you enjoy it as much as we enjoyed crafting it.

- speed improvements
- bug fixes

- New missions
- Manual transactions, bills, and income
- New spending analysis
- Fixes and speed improvements
- Update to onboarding
Updates for iOS 11

- Updates to Albert Genius
- Speed improvements and bug fixes

Albert Genius now includes Investments, here first on iOS!
• No matter your budget or experience, your money works harder with our commission-free, guided investing service.
• Select and manage your own funds. Or, tell us about your goals and receive a Genius portfolio customized to your profile in minutes.
• And, don’t miss the interactive Genius tab. Get help with the financial topics you care about most.
• As always, enjoy our latest handful of tweaks and bug fixes.

Albert now negotiates bills on your behalf – stop overpaying for your cell phone, cable, security and other bills. Connect your bank account and credit cards, and we'll find your bills and negotiate the lowest rate for you. We've also made speed improvements and a handful of bug fixes to improve your experience. We hope you enjoy it!

- An updated budget, with future income and bills, and a new section for savings
